### Health check
GET http://localhost:8787/health

### Database health check
GET http://localhost:8787/health/db

### Not found test
GET http://localhost:8787/unknown

### Get all items
GET http://localhost:8787/items

### Create item
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Milk",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "liter",
  "refillFrequencyDays": 3,
  "lowStockThreshold": 0.5
}

### Update item quantity
PATCH http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/quantity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### Delete item
DELETE http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Get suggestions
GET http://localhost:8787/suggestions

### Create refill-due item
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Coffee",
  "quantity": 3,
  "unit": "packs",
  "lastBoughtAt": "2026-03-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "refillFrequencyDays": 7,
  "lowStockThreshold": 1
}

### Get daily summary
GET http://localhost:8787/summary/daily

### Create low stock item
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sugar",
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit": "kg",
  "lowStockThreshold": 2
}
###
POST http://localhost:8787/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pepper",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Snooze item for today
POST http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/snooze

### Mark item as bought today
POST http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/bought

### Get derived cadence for item
GET http://localhost:8787/items/REPLACE_WITH_ID/cadence
